sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as MLflow SDK / Browser
    participant Gateway as ODH Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Auth as K8s Auth Plugin<br/>before_request handler
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant WS as Workspace Provider<br/>namespace mapping
    participant Server as MLflow Server<br/>5000/TCP HTTP
    participant DB as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: User Experiment Tracking Request

    Client->>Gateway: POST /mlflow/api/2.0/mlflow/runs/create<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)<br/>Header: X-MLFLOW-WORKSPACE
    Gateway->>Server: HTTP/5000 Forward<br/>Bearer Token forwarded
    Server->>Auth: before_request hook
    Auth->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>TLS 1.2+ / SA token
    K8sAPI-->>Auth: Allowed/Denied
    Auth->>WS: Resolve workspace from header
    WS->>K8sAPI: Namespace validation<br/>TLS 1.2+ / SA token
    K8sAPI-->>WS: Namespace exists
    WS-->>Server: Workspace context set
    Server->>DB: INSERT run record<br/>Workspace-scoped query
    DB-->>Server: Run ID
    Server->>S3: PUT artifact<br/>AWS credentials / TLS 1.2+
    S3-->>Server: OK
    Server-->>Gateway: JSON Response (Run metadata)
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: AI Gateway LLM Invocation

    participant LLM as LLM Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Client->>Gateway: POST /mlflow/gateway/{endpoint}/mlflow/invocations<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)
    Gateway->>Server: HTTP/5000 Forward
    Server->>Auth: before_request hook
    Auth->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview
    K8sAPI-->>Auth: Allowed
    Server->>DB: SELECT provider config<br/>KEK-encrypted credentials
    DB-->>Server: Encrypted config
    Note over Server: Decrypt API key<br/>AES-256-GCM + PBKDF2<br/>600K iterations
    Server->>LLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>TLS 1.2+ / Decrypted API key
    LLM-->>Server: LLM Response (streaming)
    Server-->>Gateway: Proxied Response
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: OTLP Trace Ingestion

    participant App as Instrumented Application

    App->>Gateway: POST /mlflow/v1/traces<br/>OTLP/HTTP protobuf<br/>Auth: Bearer Token + x-mlflow-experiment-id
    Gateway->>Server: HTTP/5000 Forward
    Server->>Auth: Validate token + experiment scope
    Auth->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview
    K8sAPI-->>Auth: Allowed
    Server->>DB: INSERT trace spans<br/>Workspace-scoped
    DB-->>Server: Trace ID
    Server->>S3: PUT trace artifacts<br/>AWS credentials / TLS 1.2+
    S3-->>Server: OK
    Server-->>Gateway: 200 OK
    Gateway-->>App: HTTPS Response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 4: Workspace Resolution (Background)

    WS->>K8sAPI: LIST/WATCH namespaces<br/>TLS 1.2+ / SA token
    K8sAPI-->>WS: Namespace list (cached)
    WS->>K8sAPI: WATCH MLflowConfig CRDs<br/>TLS 1.2+ / SA token
    K8sAPI-->>WS: MLflowConfig updates
    Note over WS: Map namespace → workspace<br/>Apply per-namespace artifact overrides
